description: The fund invests in equity securities of companies substantially in the same proportion as its underlying index, which measures the performance of Canadian oil and gas companies in the midstream sector that are listed on the TSX. Constituents are selected based on size and liquidity requirements, with a minimum number of 10 constituents in the portfolio. The fund is weighted equally and rebalanced on a quarterly basis.
name: Horizons Pipelines & Energy Services Index ETF
